Portugal cement consumption up 25 pct yr / yr June . Consumption of cement in Portugal in June rose to a record level of 831 , 000 tonnes , 25 percent more than in June 1996 , the Association of Construction and Public Works Companies ( AECOPS ) said . " The 831 , 000 tonnes of cement that AECOPS estimates were consumed in June represent an all - time high for consumption as compared with June in previous years , and the year - on - year increase was 25 percent , " a statement said . Consumption of cement in the first six months of 1997 grew by 20 . 5 percent year - on - year to 4 . 723 million tonnes , AECOPS said . 
